## Conditional command connected to an event.

MyButton:

<MyButton@Button>:
	text: "Push Me, Baby"
	italic: True
	font_size: 60
	on_press:
		if self.font_size < 70: print("This button text is SO BIG!")
		self.font_size = 100
		self.text = "You Pushed Me!"
	on_release:
		self.font_size = 60
		self.text = "Push Me, Baby"
		print("No, it's not.")

